{"tid":316702,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"見此POST既DSE巴絲，聽日放榜準備夢想成真!","createTime":"2017-07-11T02:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T00:56:27.000Z","uid":65930,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc9a3760cdae5ab34d7f4086b272be04cd5a29c","tid":316702,"uid":65930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:37:42.000Z","msg":"聽日就放榜喇，<br />\n咁多位巴絲係咪好緊張呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係度預祝咁多位聽日放榜心想事成，<br />\n入到心儀既大學/得到理想既成績<br />\n由準大學生變成真正既大學生!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但點都好，<br />\n記住hope for the best, prepare for the worst,<br />\n萬一成績唔似預期，唔好掛住喊，<br />\n記得捉住D老師問下意見，睇下點樣改jupas,<br />\n相信唔少巴絲都做左兩手準備，<br />\n教統局亦準備左<br />\n「e導航」、「712升學及就業地圖」同埋「2017放榜指南針」三個APPS，<br />\n巴絲打都可以dl定落黎睇下岩唔岩用，<br />\n唔好兩手空空返學校，<br />\n記得準備定:<br />\n一支水，<br />\n一把遮，<br />\n一部風扇仔，<br />\n一個尿袋，<br />\n少量文具，<br />\n千零蚊，<br />\n高中成績表/證書<br />\n同埋記得要積極面對呀!<br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲真係覺得好緊張好徬徨，有D咩想搵個過來人傾下，<br />\n可以telegram: buttonwood<br />\n<br />\n亦都歡迎大家放榜後係度分享好消息!<br />\n預祝各位成功!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df0b9d54d233ed9792921091685e922d8ace6e2","tid":316702,"uid":65930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"文憑試放榜準備清單 學友社<br />\n<a href=\"http://student.hk/site/?q=article/1337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstudent.hk%2Fsite%2F%3Fq%3Darticle%2F1337&d=4OnnOyGQHbV%2FZoZkzvCjlkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5f1fd58c\" target=\"_blank\">http://student.hk/site/?q=article/1337</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學友社網頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.student.hk/site/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.student.hk%2Fsite%2F&d=4OnnOyGQHbV%2FZoZkzvCjlkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=40280197\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.student.hk/site/</a><br />\n<br />\n學友社學生專線<br />\n25033399 (一三五晚7-9點)